node.text: It’s crazy how @illiminate started as an idea. Here’s a little reminder to not let fear hold you back. Everything you truly want and deserve is on the other side of fear. Believe in yourself. It’s normal to be scared. That’s what makes us human. Our lowest days helps us appreciate our best. YOU GOT THIS! I believe in YOU!
